textBeforeTable: Standings are calculated based on points accrued in the Adult Amateur Hunter division with either a horse or a pony. Points are awarded based on the placing of a horse/rider combination and the number of entries shown in the first performance class of each section. A horse/rider combination will receive one point for each entry they placed above. For example, if there are fifteen entries in the class, first place receives fourteen points, second receives thirteen points, third receives twelve points, and so forth. A horse/rider combination placing fifteenth in the class will not receive any points. 2015 SmartPak Adult Amateur Hunter Standings
